  "det_check_template": "proof fn det_test(self_: Bitmap, index: usize, r1: Result<bool, Error>, r2: Result<bool, Error>)\n    requires self_.inv(),\n    ensures\n        (match r1 {\n                Ok(b_1) => {\n                    &&& index < self_@.num_bits\n                    &&& b_1 == self_@.is_bit_set(index as int)\n                },\n                Err(_) => index >= self_@.num_bits,\n            }\n        && match r2 {\n                Ok(b_2) => {\n                    &&& index < self_@.num_bits\n                    &&& b_2 == self_@.is_bit_set(index as int)\n                },\n                Err(_) => index >= self_@.num_bits,\n            }\n        {ASSUMES})\n        ==> r1 == r2\n{\n}",
